OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784272687
OL,3,CMum says she's 'done with
OL,4,Cincompetency' of SEND services
OL,6,FCharlie Mead, from Minehead, is a
OL,7,Fmother of two children with specialist
OL,8,Feducational needs, and says that her
OL,9,Feldest child was "incredibly let down
OL,10,Fby the system".
OL,12,FMs Mead says that the same situation
OL,13,Fis also happening with her youngest
OL,14,Fchild.
OL,16,F"It's like deja vu, they say the
OL,17,Fsystem has improved but it really
OL,18,Fhasn't in the nine years I've had this
OL,19,Ffight. I'm just done, absolutely done
OL,20,Fwith the incompetency," she said.
OL,26,@xD@MrrxD@Oqp
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
