OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784272687
OL,3,CMum says she's 'done with
OL,4,Cincompetency' of SEND services
OL,6,FInternal reports from Somerset Council
OL,7,Frecently revealed a crisis within the
OL,8,Fspecial educational needs and
OL,9,Fdisabilities (SEND) services, with
OL,10,Finternal management conflict and
OL,11,Funequal workload distribution, leading
OL,12,Fto a mass exodus of experienced case
OL,13,Fofficers.
OL,15,FLast week, the council approved a #5.3
OL,16,Fmillion one-off 'recovery funding'
OL,17,Fpackage to improve SEND support over
OL,18,Fthe next two years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784272687
OL,3,CMum says she's 'done with
OL,4,Cincompetency' of SEND services
OL,6,FCharlie took her youngest son,
OL,7,FSullivan, out of mainstream school
OL,8,Fafter finding that "it didn't work"
OL,9,Ffor him.
OL,11,F"From January 2025 to March there were
OL,12,Ffive suspensions and he was lying in
OL,13,Fbed just going 'I'm a really bad
OL,14,Fchild', and I was just thinking 'I
OL,15,Fcan't do this'," she said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
