PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784272687
OL,3,CMum says she's 'done with
OL,4,Cincompetency' of SEND services
OL,6,FSullivan managed to get a place at an
OL,7,Falternative provision (AP), which
OL,8,Fwhile his mum says "has made the world
OL,9,Fof difference", it's just a "stopgap"
OL,10,Funtil her son secures a place at a
OL,11,Fschool that caters to his needs.
OL,13,FMs Mead explained to ITV News that
OL,14,Fbecause her son needs some transition
OL,15,Ftime to get settled in a new school,
OL,16,FCharlie says it's now too late for him
OL,17,Fto switch to the desired school, so
OL,18,Fhas applied for him to spend another
OL,19,Fyear at the AP.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
