PN,40405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784272687
OL,3,CMum says she's 'done with
OL,4,Cincompetency' of SEND services
OL,6,F"As of yet, nothing, I haven't heard a
OL,7,Fword," she said.
OL,9,F"We had an emergency ECHP meeting in
OL,10,FApril 2025 where I was told Sullivan
OL,11,Fwas on the priority list for September
OL,12,Fthat year, but it's still not resolved.
OL,14,F"He doesn't have any place for this
OL,15,FSeptember, let alone that September."
OL,17,FAn education, health and care plan
OL,18,F(EHCP) is a structured plan that
OL,19,Foutlines the provisions that a child
OL,20,Fneeds to meet their educational
OL,21,Frequirements.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784272687
OL,3,CMum says she's 'done with
OL,4,Cincompetency' of SEND services
OL,6,FAccording to the internal report, the
OL,7,Fcouncil's average wait time for an
OL,8,FEHCP is 51 weeks, with a backlog of
OL,9,F618 assessments sitting in the system.
OL,11,FCharlie and a group of parents held a
OL,12,Fpeaceful protest outside of Somerset
OL,13,FCouncil today (16 July).
OL,15,F"I want our voices heard," Charlie
OL,16,Fsaid. "When you see these stories you
OL,17,Fthink it's just one person but it's
OL,18,Fnot, there are hundreds of us.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784272687
OL,3,CMum says she's 'done with
OL,4,Cincompetency' of SEND services
OL,6,F"It's a legal right for children to
OL,7,Fhave an education. Every other child
OL,8,Fwho is neurotypical and doesn't have a
OL,9,Fdisability has a school place in
OL,10,FSeptember, where's ours?"
OL,12,FCllr Bill Revans, leader of Somerset
OL,13,FCouncil, told ITV News: "We've had a
OL,14,Fparticularly difficult time for our
OL,15,FSEND service, we've seen a massive
OL,16,Fincrease in applications for education
OL,17,Fand healthcare plans.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784272687
OL,3,CMum says she's 'done with
OL,4,Cincompetency' of SEND services
OL,6,F"We've put in an additional #5.7
OL,7,Fmillion to try and get those transfer
OL,8,Fplaces sorted for September but we're
OL,9,Faware that we are disappointing some
OL,10,Fparents and we truly apologise for the
OL,11,Funcertainty that that's caused, it's
OL,12,Fcertainly not acceptable."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
